  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the time when my father was working in [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Herford. ?] And the people who, the old people who still lived in their house there, they-- they-- they were outside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all what we heard was screaming and the [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "SR, ?] you know, in the ghetto uniforms [? was ?] outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they broke everything in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not, ghetto.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "SR ?] uniform.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "SA, there was the yellow uniforms they had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not the SS, had the black uniforms and the gray ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was the [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "SR, ?] I think, was the storm troopers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they destroyed the whole--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Destroyed the whole house on the inside completely, the furniture, [INAUDIBLE], everything what we had was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, from then on, we really lived in broken-up pieces already till they took us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the last day of school, the German school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They broke-- they didn't put it in fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They broke it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think I have pictures in the album there I can show you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The few stores, which they--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They arrested-- they arrested all the men, mostly all the men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were sent to Buchenwald and Auschwitz-- Buchenwald and Dachau at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A few did not come back already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a younger man, I remember, his name was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Antz ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Swatchauer. ?] He was married to one of the Groontman girls in our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- they arrested him, and he went to-- to-- he went to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were notified that he died there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or he got killed in Dachau then already in '38.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That's [SIGHS] another story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
